title: How Much PXSeal Should We Send to The Burn Address?
body:
The DeFi 3.0 Treasury will market buy PXSeal and burn it, how much should we burn?

The burn will occur on Christmas Eve (00:00 UTC) Midnight - 12/24/2020 to allow member of the ecosystem time to get into this coin.
author: 0x51077888D2bb2b36b28925bd204b50c6B9E96D69
